    sh:message "Special-category PII (GDPR Article 10) MUST have an associated dpv:hasLegalBasis triple. ODR-0012 Phase 1 + ODR-0013 §Q1 Category 4: lawful-basis-elevated PII is a Violation-tier breach."@en ;
